<emphasis bold="true" box="[512,537,1870,1891]" pageId="18" pageNumber="419">A.</emphasis>
SMF 35008, 8.8 cm SL, Jizan, Saudi Arabia. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1014,1038,1870,1891]" pageId="18" pageNumber="419">B.</emphasis>
